# Nyaya AI 🏛️

> Upload any Indian legal document and get plain English summaries + ask questions about it.

## 🚀 Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** React + Tailwind CSS
- **Backend:** FastAPI
- **LLM:** Llama 3 (via Groq API)
- **Vector DB:** ChromaDB
- **Embeddings:** sentence-transformers

## ✨ Features
- [ ] Upload legal PDFs (FIR, rental agreements, court orders)
- [ ] Plain English / Hindi summaries
- [ ] Ask questions about the document
- [ ] RAG-powered accurate responses

